B.M9=new A.cr("The Sound","Fibrillations sound like 'rain on a tin roof'. PSWs sound like a 'dull thud'.")
B.LH=new A.cr("The Look","Fibrillations are brief spikes (1-5ms) with an initial positive (downward) deflection. PSWs have that same initial positive spike followed by a slow, sweeping negative return.")
B.LO=new A.cr("The Rate","Regular, rhythmic firing between 0.5-10Hz.")
