B.ac0=new A.bY("Which nerve root is most commonly affected in cervical radiculopathy?",B.ZQ,2,"C7 is the most commonly affected cervical nerve root (approx 70%), usually presenting with triceps weakness.")
B.a24=s(["Weakness of ankle dorsiflexion","Loss of patellar reflex","Loss of Achilles reflex","Sensory loss on the medial calf"],t.s)
